org.knime.core.node.workflow

Class EditorUIInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.core.node.workflow.EditorUIInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, UIInformation

    public class EditorUIInformation
extends Object
implements UIInformation
    Stores workflow editor specific settings (like grid settings and zoom level, etc.). Can be attached to the node UI info object of workflow managers.
    Since:
    2.6
    Author:
    Peter Ohl, KNIME.com AG, Zurich, Switzerland
